ass=\"feature-title body-copy v-fw-medium\" style=\"line-height: normal; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 11px 0px 6px;\">Cinematic Infinity Displays</h4><p class=\"body-copy\" style=\"margin-bottom: 9px; line-height: normal;\">Refined form meets cinematic brilliance with an expansive 7.6” Dynamic AMOLED screen⁴ bringing you an expansive cinematic display that fits in your pocket.</p></div><div class=\"list-row\"><h4 class=\"feature-title body-copy v-fw-medium\" style=\"line-height: normal; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 11px 0px 6px;\">Flex UI</h4><p class=\"body-copy\" style=\"margin-bottom: 9px; line-height: normal;\">Elevate your gaming and binge-watching experience with smooth motion, fluid scrolling and flawless effects on the 7.6\" Infinity Display with 120Hz refresh rate⁵.</p></div><div class=\"list-row\"><h4 class=\"feature-title body-copy v-fw-medium\" style=\"line-height: normal; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 11px 0px 6px;\">Adaptive Display</h4><p class=\"body-copy\" style=\"margin-bottom: 9px; line-height: normal;\">Galaxy Z Fold2 5G brings seamless integration of hardware and software for a transformative mobile experience. Multi-task with multiple apps, enjoy wireless productivity, and dominate the competition with powerful gaming.</p></div><div class=\"list-row\"><h4 class=\"feature-title body-copy v-fw-medium\" style=\"line-height: normal; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 11px 0px 6px;\">Enhanced Multi-tasking</h4><p class=\"body-copy\" style=\"margin-bottom: 9px; line-height: normal;\">Galaxy Z Fold2 5G invigorates the multifaceted work and thought that defines your life. Easily transition between both displays with App Continuity.⁷Multi Active Window⁶ gives you the power to navigate, drag and-drop and work across three apps on the expansive main display.</p></div><div class=\"list-row\"><h4 class=\"feature-title body-copy v-fw-medium\" style=\"line-height: normal; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 11px 0px 6px;\">Enhanced Play</h4><p class=\"body-copy\" style=\"margin-bottom: 9px; line-height: normal;\">Cutting-edge performance, long-lasting battery life, and an expansive 120Hz refresh rate display make Galaxy Z Fold2 5G the perfect addition to any gamer\'s arsenal.</p></div><div class=\"list-row\"><h4 class=\"feature-title body-copy v-fw-medium\" style=\"line-height: normal; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 11px 0px 6px;\">Plenty of Memory and Storage</h4><p class=\"body-copy\" style=\"margin-bottom: 9px; line-height: normal;\">With 12GB of RAM for intensive multitasking — from gaming to streaming, and even live broadcasting all at once. Plus, 256GB built in storage is ample space for your apps and media.</p></div><div class=\"list-row\"><h4 class=\"feature-title body-copy v-fw-medium\" style=\"line-height: normal; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 11px 0px 6px;\">Productivity &amp; Play</h4><p class=\"body-copy\" style=\"margin-bottom: 9px; line-height: normal;\">Fold your GalaxyZFold2 5G and select apps will automatically adjust to take advantage of the innovative form factor. Enjoy streamlined experiences and preview apps on one half while controlling with the other whether it\'s videochatting, watching Youtube videos, or editing videos.</p></div><div class=\"list-row\"><h4 class=\"feature-title body-copy v-fw-medium\" style=\"line-height: normal; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 11px 0px 6px;\">2-in-1 Experience</h4><p class=\"body-copy\" style=\"margin-bottom: 9px; line-height: normal;\">With Galaxy Z Fold2 5G 5G you can have it all and do it all. Folded it\'s a phone - unfolded it\'s a tablet.</p></div><div class=\"list-row\"><h4 class=\"feature-title body-copy v-fw-medium\" style=\"line-height: normal; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 11px 0px 6px;\">Intelligent Battery</h4><p class=\"body-copy\" style=\"margin-bottom: 9px; line-height: normal;\">Galaxy Z Fold2 5G\'s revolutionary battery is a game-changer, combining the energy from two batteri